      "modified": "2026-04-26T18:48:00.000Z",
      "content": "Investigation by GHOST/Breakglass Intelligence on 2026-04-26. C2 at 31.58.220.250 was offline at time of investigation (all ports closed). Infrastructure was active from approximately 2026-03-05 to sometime before 2026-04-26 (~52 days). Source tip from @skocherhan. ThreatFox coverage via DonPasci. Iran nexus: OTX geolocates IP to Iran, zeosshop.ir is an Iranian domain behind ArvanCloud CDN.",
